data.description: Beautiful home with unobstructed views! NO HOA's! Well cared for, single level home with vaulted ceilings and easy handicap accessibility. Amazing views from your private, over-sized, fenced backyard. Short walk to Southview Trailhead, plus miles of hiking and mountain biking trails. Shopping and restaurants just minutes away. Come enjoy living in this friendly, quiet neighborhood. Located within minutes of downtown Cedar City and Southern Utah University. Great investment or rental property. Condition of Sale: Seller intends to lease-back property until 7/31/2024 @ $1,800 per month.
